Changes for the Labyrinth-Plugin-Wiki
=====================================

        - fixed distribution name in META (thanks Neil).

1.04    2013-05-05
        - change file dates changed to meet W3CDTF standards.
        - fixed site and link pattern matching.
        - use process_html from MLUtils rather than handcrafting.
        - upgrade to Labyrinth 5.16.
        - updated templates.
        - added LICENSE file.

1.03    2012-06-07
        - META tests no longer require specific versions.
        - added minimum perl version (5.006).
        - reworked Makefile.PL for clarity.

1.02    2011-06-19
        - URL pattern update to accept '/' in text alternative.
        - update to Single/Pair balancing in XHTML.
        - added documentation.

1.01    2011-05-08
        - cleaned up phrasebook.ini.
        - URL pattern match fixes.
        - WikiLink now only checks whether a linked page exists.

1.00    2011-01-19
        - first official release
